Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OTPClient
    This is the one-time-pad client, it requests a port number, a remote host, a hex seed for SecureRandom, and a message to be transmitted.
    OTPCrypt
    Utility class mostly used by the one-time-pad server and client for encrypting and decrypting messages.
    OTPServer
    This is the one-time-pad server, it requests a port number, and a hex seed for SecureRandom.
    OTPServerThread
    Thread generated when a client connects.
